BUG-03: Confusing Date of Birth Validation Error

Severity: Medium

Environment: Windows 11, Chrome Browser

Steps to Reproduce (STR):

1)Navigate to the "Sign-up & Profile Wizard."

2)In the "Date of Birth" field, enter a nonsensical future year like 275760.

Expected Result: A clear error like "Invalid date" or "Date cannot be in the future" should be displayed.

Actual Result: A pop-up alert appears with the irrelevant message "Must be 18+."

Evidence:
 ![Screenshot showing Confusing Date of Birth](evidence\bug-03-ecced-year.png)